Class ParkingSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • airport.ParkingSystem

  • public class ParkingSystem
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing the overall parking business. Keeps info about the various parking lots we have. When vehicles enter the system, their number plates are recorded by cameras and a Vehicle record is created if we haven't seen it before. This enables us to prevent vehicles being in two places at the same time, and similar problems.

    kki32
